! --- skravering
poly2_b 10, 1+2+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0.276, 0.154976, 1, 0.277843, 0.30013, 1, 0.263731, 0.321581, 1, 0.223, 0.336084, 1, -0.181866, 0.336123, 1, -0.223731, 0.321581, 1, -0.240438, 0.294723, 1, -0.187, -1.303922, 1, 0.233, -1.303922, 1, 0.276, 0.154976, -1 else ! --- 1/200 --- add2 -0.239, -1.303922 POLY2_B 5, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0, 0, 1, a, 0, 1, a, b, 1, 0, b, 1, 0, 0, -1

endif
if iSymbolType = 2 then ! Type 2 POLY2_ 5, 1, 0.06, b-0.48, 1, a-0.06, b-0.48, 1, a-0.06, b-0.06, 1, 0.06, b-0.06, 1, 0.06, b-0.48, -1 endif
if iSymbolType = 3 then ! Type 3 LINE2 a, 0, 0, b endif
else ! --- 1/100 --- if det2D = 2 then line2 0, b*11/12, a, b*11/12 line2 0, b*11/12, a, b*11/12 endif endif del 1 endif
! --- Minimal Space ---
DRAWINDEX 10 reqBMinSpace = 0 add2 -0.233, -1.303922 call "fa_minimalspace" parameters all MSType = 3, unID = 3000, returned_parameters reqBMinSpace, MSFillType, MSFillPen, MSFillBackPen, MSContLineType, MSContLinePen
!if reqBMinSpace <> 0 and (MSFront > EPS or MSSide > EPS or MSRear > EPS)then ! FILL MSFillType ! PEN MSContLinePen ! line_type MSContLineType ! ! POLY2_B 7, 1+2+4+64, MSFillPen, MSFillBackPen, ! 0,0,(MSSide < EPS), ! 0, B,(MSRear < EPS), ! A, B,(MSSide < EPS), ! A,0,(MSFront < EPS), ! 0,0,-1, ! A/2, A/2, 900, ! A/2, 360, 4000 !endif
